casebody.data:
DISCIPLINARY CASES

2009-1145. Cleveland Metro. Bar Assn. v. Nance.

It is ordered by this court, sua sponte, that Donald S. Nance, Attorney Registration No. 0034086, last known business address in Cleveland, Ohio, is found in contempt for failure to comply with this court’s order of November 19, 2009, to wit: failure to file an affidavit of compliance on or before December 21, 2009, and failure to pay board costs in the amount of $1,621.28 on or before February 17, 2010.
